urgund.", "-Og videre?", "-I morgen drar jeg til Champagne, s\u00e5 jeg f\u00e5r vel anledning til \u00e5 feire videre der, sier den nybakte Master of Wine-innehaveren."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "kultur|vin"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "a758b76ab7d91362d178ebd503642f94f85b4658814bdadafcb2d8086ea75d9c"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-30T19:30:30.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Norge har f\u00e5tt sin tredje Master of Wine (MN). Denne uken besto Sebastian Bredal den siste eksamenen i verdens t\u00f8ffeste vinutdannelse."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/d2ddc1437140fb5bab7a0cc1d953cb273aa4ee87.jpg?5984ba78"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Bredal ble Master of Wine nr. 3 -adressa.no", "Feirer i Volnay", "Ronold var f\u00f8rst", "Feirer med 1972-flaske"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "d2ddc1437140fb5bab7a0cc1d953cb273aa4ee87"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["vinpuls", "vinklubb", "ulf dalheim", "vin", "database"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "vinpuls,vinklubb,ulf dalheim,vin,database"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["kultur", "vin"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "food-and-drink"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "vinmonopolet"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["master of", "master"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["master of wine", "burgund", "symposium wines", "arcus gruppen", "volnay", "vinforum", "champagne", "vinpuls", "adresseavisens", "may tjensland master", "may tjensland master of wine", "master"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["norge", "norden"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["arne rono